    "However, the few occurrences that were observed highlight the necessity for ongoing quality control and updates to the tutor bot's knowledge base.",
    "Ensuring the accuracy and reliability of information is essential to building and maintaining students' trust in the tutor bot as a dependable learning resource.",
    "Figure 3 illustrates this issue.",
    "Earlier in the conversation, the student introduced the topic of the law on the promotion of family education.",
    "However, when the tutor bot inquired about strategies and methods for improving teaching quality and student learning outcomes, it posed a question that was irrelevant to the topic of family education policy."
